    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Clean, honest good-condition car that runs and drives well and presents nicely for its age. It has clearly been kept up better than an average older used vehicle, with a solid overall appearance inside and out, though you should still expect normal cosmetic wear and minor age-related imperfections. This is a dependable everyday driver, not a showroom car, but it\u2019s in the kind of condition most buyers will feel good about owning and using right away.",
