      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable runaround or a project with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great opportunity for someone who wants dependable basic transport without spending a fortune. It\u2019s priced to reflect its condition, and with a bit of TLC it could make a really handy daily, first car, or weekend fixer-upper. Honest sale, friendly seller, and a great chance to grab a budget-friendly motor with life left in it.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Strong-running project with solid drivetrain character and plenty of usable life left for the right owner. Engine fires up eagerly, transmission engages, and the chassis has the kind of honest mechanical feel enthusiasts appreciate in a budget platform. Not a showpiece, but a capable driver/project candidate with good bones, attractive stance, and real upside for someone who knows their way around maintenance and light reconditioning. A great opportunity to get into an affordable car with presence and potential without spending big money.",
